    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Depends on the use case, the most common error being \"I want a filter on attribute `color`\" and the attribute is not declared as attributes for faceting.\n\nWe can find from the answer that there's no response for \"color\" because it's not configured.\n\nI only wonder if we can distinguish \"not configured\" from \"no facet values given the context\"\n",
